---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Boomger."
  slug="privacy-policy"
  description="Learn how Boomger collects, uses, protects, and handles your personal data. Our Privacy Policy explains your rights and data protection practices."
>
  <main
    class="pt-10 pb-24 mx-6 sm:mx-12 lg:mx-24 max-w-5xl text-zinc-900 leading-relaxed"
  >
    <!-- Intro -->
    <section class="space-y-4 mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Privacy Policy for Boomger
      </h1>

      <p class="text-zinc-600 font-medium">Effective Date: 05 June 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold pt-4">Introduction</h2>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        Welcome to Boomger. Your privacy is important to us, and we are
        committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains
        how Boomger collects, uses, discloses, and safeguards your information
        when you use our dating application.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        By using Boomger, you agree to the collection and use of information in
        accordance with this Privacy Policy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 1 -->
    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">1. Information We Collect</h2>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        We collect several types of information for various purposes to provide
        and improve our services.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pt-2">
        a. Information You Provide to Us
      </h3>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Account Information:</strong> Personal
        details such as name, email, phone number, date of birth, gender, and
        registration data.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Profile Information:</strong> Photos,
        interests, location, education, bio, and optional personal details.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Payment Information:</strong> Billing and
        transaction details when purchasing subscriptions (processed via
        third-party providers).
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pt-2">
        b. Information We Collect Automatically
      </h3>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Usage Data:</strong> Matches, messages,
        app interactions, and feature usage.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Device Information:</strong> IP address,
        device type, operating system, app version, and browser type.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pt-2">
        c. Information from Third Parties
      </h3>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Connected Accounts:</strong> Data from
        social media or external services when you choose to link them.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 2 -->
    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-zinc-700">
        <li>Operate and maintain Boomger</li>
        <li>Manage user accounts</li>
        <li>Personalize user experience</li>
        <li>Enable location-based features</li>
        <li>Process payments</li>
        <li>Send notifications and updates</li>
        <li>Provide customer support</li>
        <li>Improve safety and performance</li>
        <li>Enforce policies and legal obligations</li>
        <li>Protect users and platform integrity</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- 3 -->
    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">3. How We Share Your Information</h2>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">With Other Users:</strong> Profile data
        visible according to your privacy settings.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">With Service Providers:</strong> Trusted
        partners handling hosting, payments, analytics, and support.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">For Legal Reasons:</strong> When required
        by law or to protect safety and rights.
      </p>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        <strong class="text-zinc-900">Business Transfers:</strong> In case of
        acquisition, merger, or restructuring.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 4 -->
    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">4. Security of Your Information</h2>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        We use appropriate safeguards to protect your data. However, no system
        can guarantee 100% security.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 5 -->
    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">5. Your Data Protection Rights</h2>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-zinc-700">
        <li>Right to access your data</li>
        <li>Right to correct inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Right to request deletion</li>
        <li>Right to restrict processing</li>
        <li>Right to data portability</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- 6 -->
    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">6. Childrenâ€™s Privacy</h2>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        Boomger is strictly for users aged 18+. Any underage data discovered
        will be deleted.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 7 -->
    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        We may update this policy. Continued use means acceptance of the updated
        version.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 8 -->
    <section class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">8. Contact Us</h2>

      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        Phone: +1 204 294 8814<br />
         Email: <a
          href="mailto:info@boomger.com"
          class="underline font-medium hover:text-black">info@boomger.com</a
        >
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
